com.interpss.core.acsc.fault
Interface AcscBusFault

All Superinterfaces:
AcscBusRef, BusRef, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Subinterfaces:
AcscBranchFault
All Known Implementing Classes:
AcscBranchFaultImpl, AcscBusFaultImpl
public interface AcscBusFault
extends AcscBusRef

A representation of the model object 'Bus Fault'. A class to describe a bus fault. The fault id = busId+faultCode.

The following features are supported:

  • Fault Type
  • Fault Code
  • ZLG Fault
  • ZLL Fault
  • Fault Result
